## Standard Prompts by Work Type

### Python / FastAPI Work

Generate implementation:
```
Implement [feature description] for OP-[ID].
Stack: Python FastAPI, Pydantic v2, async endpoints.
Create: src/[module]/[filename].py
Include pytest tests at: tests/test_[filename].py
Follow all rules from CLAUDE.md.
```

Generate tests:
```
Write pytest tests for [function/class] in OP-[ID].
Cover: happy path, edge cases, error handling.
Target coverage: >80%.
```

