## Commit and Branch Generators

Ask Claude to generate the branch name:
```
Generate branch name for OP-[ID]: [paste task subject]
Work type: feature / task / fix
```

Ask Claude to generate commit message:
```
Generate commit message for OP-[ID].
Changes made: [briefly describe]
```

Expected format:
  Branch:  feature/OP-42-sellout-weekly-mart
  Commit:  feat(OP-42): add mart_sellout_weekly with brand split

