## Branch & Commit Reference

| Work type      | Branch format          | Commit prefix    |
|----------------|------------------------|------------------|
| BI Feature     | feature/OP-42-name     | feat(OP-42):     |
| BI Task        | task/OP-87-name        | task(OP-87):     |
| Bug fix        | fix/OP-103-name        | fix(OP-103):     |
| Refactor       | feature/OP-42-name     | refactor(OP-42): |

