## Status Reference (automatic — you do nothing)

| You do                           | OP status becomes                      |
|----------------------------------|----------------------------------------|
| Push to feature/OP-42-*          | AUTO: In Progress                      |
| Open PR with "Closes OP #42"    | AUTO: In Testing                       |
| PR merged to main               | AUTO: Tested + GCP deploy triggered    |
| PR closed without merge          | AUTO: Rejected                         |
| Tests fail on push               | AUTO: Bug WP created as child of OP-42 |

PM manually sets Closed after verifying on production.

